flowchart LR
  I["Bash Intent"] --> S["Schema\ncommand/timeout/cwd"]
  S --> A["Static Analysis\n解析命令"]
  A --> P{"Permission\nallow/ask/deny"}
  P -->|deny| R["Reject"]
  P -->|ask| H["Human Confirm"]
  H -->|拒绝| R
  H -->|同意| W["Sandbox Decision"]
  P -->|allow| W
  W --> X["Spawn Process\n受控执行"]
  X --> O["Output Capture\nstdout/stderr/exit"]
  O --> B{"Too Large?"}
  B -->|yes| K["Persist + Preview"]
  B -->|no| N["Return Observation"]
  K --> N

  A:::hot
  P:::hot
  W:::hot

  classDef hot fill:#fff3b0,stroke:#111,stroke-width:2px,color:#111;
